    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owner. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts as it should, and all major electronic features are fully functional. While the interior is clean and smoke-free, you may find some minor cosmetic wear consistent with responsible use, such as light seat bolsters wear and a few small stone chips on the hood. It serves as a reliable, high-quality option for anyone looking for a dependable vehicle that still looks and drives great.",
