    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for your next adventure with this fantastic, well-maintained ride! It's in good condition and has been reliably cared for, offering a smooth driving experience and a clean interior that's ready for its next owner. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that looks great and performs even better\u2014perfect for anyone looking for quality and value!",
